{"tid":2394099,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"國際培幼會遭踢爆善款60%做行政費","createTime":"2021-02-04T03:02:41.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-04T06:42:50.000Z","uid":13745,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"f6a08da750f4b9ba2cbf12b48bcf130a794ab425","tid":2394099,"uid":13745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T03:02:41.000Z","msg":"【本報訊】由藝人鄭伊健、蘇玉華擔任慈善大使的國際培幼會（香港）被質疑開支龐大，籌款成效低。監察慈善機構網站明施慎選揭發，該會前年籌款逾2,450萬元，但逾六成款項用於營運及行政開支，多達1,500萬元，市民每捐10元，不足4元用於慈善。立法會議員批評，若大部份善款用作行政費，變相呃人。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20130301/44U55MVFR2Y5O6GRQUE6GCQLHI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20130301%2F44U55MVFR2Y5O6GRQUE6GCQLHI%2F&d=LTOHNK%2B9fuVs8qin7tjZRJSOxZpZ29aBESoBY3kI%2Fuw%3D&h=0dfb7807\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20130301%2F44U55MVFR2Y5O6GRQUE6GCQLHI%2F&h=07f7cb5c\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20130301/44U55MVFR2Y5O6GRQUE6GCQLHI/</a><br />\n<br />\n根據國際培幼會（香港）提交公司註冊處的財務報告，2011年營運及行政開支約1,500萬元，當中籌款費約260萬元，佔17.6%；公關、市場推廣及出版費用高達600萬元；餘下約650萬是行政費，薪酬開支佔去六成，約400萬元。該年度籌款逾2,450萬元，最終不足四成約950萬元善款用於國際發展項目。"},{"pid":"7a813f4ebeb70798e9dd807f14c5189eefb5854c","tid":2394099,"uid":100697,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T03:05:35.000Z","msg":"2013年"},{"pid":"6168b32e903763269b69d5492d4e0d98f725f667","tid":2394099,"uid":13745,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"7a813f4ebeb70798e9dd807f14c5189eefb5854c","tid":2394099,"uid":100697,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T03:05:35.000Z","msg":"2013年"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T03:06:33.000Z","msg":"邊度有最update 盤數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93f51263d646374de55b0e9e11acf09378cb0169","tid":2394099,"uid":176910,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T03